@page
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.TagHelpers
@using Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore
@using UniversityMedicalRecord.Data
@using UniversityMedicalRecord.Models
@model UnivMedicalRecord.Pages.Homepage.ViewMedical



    @{
	    Layout = null;
    }


<style>
 
        body {
                   background-color: #8080;
                   font-family: sans-serif;
                   //text-align: center;
               }
        
               form {
                   background-color: #fff;
                   width: 1000px;
                   max-width: fit-content;
                   height: fit-content;
                   margin: 50px auto;
                   padding: 40px 20px;
                   box-shadow: 2px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
               }
           	
           	.gen-records{
           	text-align: center;
           	}
           
           
           
        
</style>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible"
          content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
	    Create General Records
    </title>
     <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-KK94CHFLLe+nY2dmCWGMq91rCGa5gtU4mk92HdvYe+M/SXH301p5ILy+dN9+nJOZ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ENjdO4Dr2bkBIFxQpeoTz1HIcje39Wm4jDKdf19U8gI4ddQ3GYNS7NTKfAdVQSZe" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
</head>

<div>
	<form class="mt-3" style="height: unset; width: unset; background-color: unset; padding: unset; margin: auto; box-shadow: unset; align-self: center" method="post">
		<div class="card" style="flex-direction: row; background-color: black; width: 1000px; align-items: center">
			<button class="btn btn-dark m-lg-3" asp-page-handler="Dashboard">Dashboard</button>
			<button class="btn btn-dark m-lg-3" asp-page-handler="LabTest">LabTest</button>
			<button class="btn btn-dark m-lg-3" asp-page-handler="Inbox">Inbox</button>
		</div>
	</form>
</div>
  
<body>
<form method="post" style="width: auto">
	<div style="text-align: center"><h3>General Records</h3><div>
			<b><div class="mb-10" style="float:left">Personal Information</div></b>
			<br/>
			<table>
				<tbody>
				<tr>
					<td> <label  class="m-lg-2"> Name: @Model.Name</label>
					</td>
					<td> <label   class="m-lg-2"> Age: @Model.Age</label>
					</td>
					<td> <div class="mt-3" style="float:left">
							<label>Gender: @Model.Sex</label>
						</div>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td> <label class="m-lg-2">Email: @Model.Email</label>
						<br/>
					</td>
					<td> <label class="m-lg-2" for="id">Id: @Model.IdNumber</label>
						<br/>
					</td>
					<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Mobile Number: @Model.MobileNumber</label>
						<br/>
					</td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td> <label for="doctor"  class="m-lg-2">Personal Doctor: @Model.Doctor</label>
						<br/>
					</td>
					<td>  <label  class="m-lg-2" >Insurance: @Model.Insurance</label>
						<br/>
					</td>
					<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Date: @Model.Date</label>
						<br/>
					</td>
    
				</tr>
				<tr>
              
					<td>  <label  class="m-lg-2" >Birth Place: @Model.BirthPlace</label>
						
					</td>
					<td>  <label  class="m-lg-2">Address: @Model.Address</label>
						
					</td>
				</tr>
    
				</tbody>
			</table>
			
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<br/>
	
	<b><div style="float:left">Mother Information</div></b>
	<br/>
	<table>
		<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Name: @Model.MotherName</label>
				
			</td>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Address: @Model.MotherAddress</label>
				
			</td>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Occupation: @Model.MotherOccupation</label>
				
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Number: @Model.MotherNumber</label>
				
			</td>
    
			<td> <div  class="m-lg-2">
					<label>Status: @Model.MotherStatus</label>
					
				</div>
			</td>
		</tr>  
		</tbody>
	</table>
		
	<br/>
	<b><div style="float:left">Father Information</div></b>
	<br/>
	<table>
		<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Name: @Model.FatherName</label>
				
			</td>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Address: @Model.FatherAddress</label>
				
			</td>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Occupation: @Model.FatherOccupation</label>
				
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Number: @Model.FatherNumber</label>
				
			</td>
    
			<td> <div >
					<label  class="m-lg-2">@Model.FatherStatus </label>
					
				</div>
			</td>
		</tr>  
		</tbody>
	</table>
	<br/>
			
	<b><div style="float:left">Guardian Information</div></b>
	<br/>
	<table>
		<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Name: @Model.GuardianName</label>
				
			</td>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Address: @Model.GuardianAddress</label>
				
			</td>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Occupation: @Model.GuardianOccupation</label>
				
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>
				
				<label class="m-lg-2">Relationship: @Model.GuardianRelation</label>
			</td>
    
			<td> 
					
					<label  class="m-lg-2">Status: @Model.GuardianStatus</label>
					<br/>
				
			</td>
		</tr>  
		</tbody>
	</table>

	<br>
	<b><div style="float:left">Medical Information</div></b>
	<br/>
	<table>
		<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Allergy: @Model.Allergy</label>
				<br/>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td> <label  class="m-lg-2">Illness: @Model.Illness</label>
				
			</td>
		</tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>
	
</form>
</body>
</html>